---
title: 配置保護鏈
description: 備份策略 → 覆蓋策略 → 還原機制
links:
  - phase-execute: 安裝執行流程
  - setup-main: 返回主流程
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph Tier1 ["Tier 1: 首次備份 (一次性)"]
        O1["pnpm run setup 首次執行"]
        O1 --> OB["~/.ab-dotfiles-original/
        ├── zshrc
        ├── zshrc.local
        ├── zsh/
        ├── claude/
        ├── zsh_history
        └── ripgreprc"]
    end

    subgraph Tier2 ["Tier 2: 增量備份 (每次 setup)"]
        S1["phaseExecute [1/8]"]
        S1 --> SB["dist/backup/YYYY-MM-DD/
        ├── claude/commands,agents,rules
        ├── hooks.json
        ├── settings.json
        ├── keybindings.json
        ├── zshrc
        ├── zshrc.local
        ├── ripgreprc
        └── zsh/modules/"]
    end

    subgraph Deploy ["覆蓋策略 (無痛遷移)"]
        D1[".zshrc
        個人設定 → .zshrc.local"]
        D2["settings.json
        smart merge (只加不刪)"]
        D3["hooks.json
        smart merge (只添加新 hook)"]
        D4["commands/agents/rules
        manifest MD5 追蹤
        用戶修改 → 跳過"]
        D5[".ripgreprc
        已有 → 跳過不動"]
        D6["modules/*.zsh
        diff 比較 → 無變更跳過"]
    end

    subgraph Restore ["還原機制"]
        R1["pnpm run restore
        ──────────
        列出所有增量備份
        選擇版本 → 還原"]
        R2["pnpm run restore-original
        ──────────
        完全回滾到安裝前狀態"]
    end

    SB --> R1
    OB --> R2
